_______________________________________________________________________________
"Animate Weapon"   
        This allows a psionicist to cause a weapon to pick itself up and
        wield itself in battle!  One of the most useful combat spells in
        the guild. It has a duration and hit points of the weapon dependent
        on the psionicist's guild level.  The psionicist must stay in the
        same room but may perform other powers, attack the monster
        himself, or whatever.  Another great advantage of this power is
        that it is not subject to weapon restrictions.  A weapon not
        normally usable by the guild MAY be animated.  If the animated 
	weapon "dies", it will be permanently broken.
 
SP Cost:  1 per second	Guild Level:  11	Potential Points:  3
 
Command:  animate <object (must be weapon)>
